{"name":"Hamburger Casserole","slug":"hamburger-casserole","description":"<p>Keep this recipe in your back pocket for busy weeknights. Itâ€™s a comfort food classic made even easier thanks to the <a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose Steamer</a>. Revamp leftover soup as a rich, tomatoey sauce to clear out your fridge and get a meal on the table STAT. Hurray for easy dinners!&nbsp;</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"uncooked macaroni or bite-size pasta","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lean ground beef","quantity":"1 lb (450 g)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Tomato Soup or Marinara Sauce","quantity":"2 cups prepared","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Tomato Soup Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"tomato paste","quantity":"1 can (6 oz/156 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"water","quantity":"4 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"heavy cream","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":"optional"},{"name":"diced tomatoes","quantity":"1 can (28 oz/796 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"crushed tomatoes","quantity":"1 can (28 oz/796 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Marinara Sauce Mix","quantity":"3 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"grated cheddar cheese","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Cook pasta in a large pot according to package directions. Drain well.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Meanwhile, place beef in&nbsp;<a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose Steamer.</a> Cover; microwave on high 4 min, or until beef is cooked through. Once cooked, carefully drain excess liquid from steamer. Use&nbsp;<a data-item-id=\"fe1c2327-1fb8-4cd2-b61a-1b1a4196ffcf\" href=\"\">Ground Meat Separator&nbsp;</a>to break up chunks.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Add cooked pasta and soup to Steamer; stir to combine. Top with cheese. Microwave, uncovered, 3 min, or until casserole is heated through and cheese is bubbly.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Let casserole rest, uncovered, 5 min, before serving.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"steamers","name":"Steamers"},{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"microwave","name":"Microwave"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"gluten_free_e8446d0","name":"Gluten-free"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"beef","name":"Beef"},{"slug":"epic_life_dinner","name":"Dinner"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":510,"fat":20,"saturatedFat":9,"transFat":0.5,"cholesterol":85,"sodium":350,"carbohydrate":51,"fiber":3,"sugars":8,"protein":32},"tips":"","perfectlyBalanceYourPlate":"<p>Serve with 1 cup steamed veggies.&nbsp;</p>"}